        "description": "FEA solver verified against NAFEMS LE1 (plane stress), LE10 (3-D solid), and T1 (thermal) benchmarks. Computed results must agree with reference solutions to within 2% for all benchmark cases. Contact formulation verified against Hertzian contact analytical solution for spherical indenter on flat substrate."
      },
      "rationale": "NAFEMS LE1, LE10, and T1 benchmarks executed; maximum deviation 1.4%. Hertzian contact patch area and peak pressure agreed with analytical solution within 1.8%. Code verification documented in Verification Report NCV-TKA-2025-03."
