        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "name": "Numerical solver error acceptance criteria — iterative convergence and contact stabilization",
        "description": "Nonlinear solution must achieve force residual norm < 1×10⁻³ and displacement increment norm < 1×10⁻⁴ at every converged increment. Contact stabilization energy must be < 1% of total strain energy. No spurious hourglassing energy in reduced-integration elements (< 0.5% of total)."
      },
      "rationale": "All load steps converged with force residual < 4×10⁻⁴ and displacement increment < 6×10⁻⁵. Contact stabilization energy 0.31% of total strain energy. Hourglass energy 0.18%. Convergence metrics archived in solver log files SL-TKA-2025-03 through SL-TKA-2025-17."
    },
    {
