        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "name": "Use error acceptance criteria — analyst qualification and model use procedure",
        "description": "Model must be operated by analysts with documented FEA training (minimum 40 hours formal training plus supervised execution of two prior orthopedic FEA projects). A written Model Use Procedure (MUP) must be in place and followed. Post-analysis checklist must be completed and archived."
      },
      "rationale": "Lead analyst holds BSME with 5 years FEA experience; secondary analyst holds MSME with orthopedic biomechanics specialization. MUP-TKA-2025-01 version 1.2 followed for all analyses. Post-analysis checklists completed and archived in project records."
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/factor/nagaraja-tka-model-form",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
